95
00:09:22,130 --> 00:09:23,760
Me and you,

96
00:09:23,760 --> 00:09:27,030
Song Ziqi, and You Keke.

97
00:09:28,370 --> 00:09:30,830
We are all going our separate ways.

98
00:09:34,490 --> 00:09:37,490
