117
00:11:07,300 --> 00:11:08,890
Zhou Siyue.

118
00:11:08,900 --> 00:11:10,770
Hey, hey, hey!

119
00:11:11,810 --> 00:11:14,400
Zhou Siyue.

120
00:11:15,710 --> 00:11:17,450
Ding Xian, you are hilarious.

121
00:11:17,450 --> 00:11:20,990
You mistook the garbage can for Zhou Siyue.

122
00:11:20,990 --> 00:11:24,000
He is Zhou Siyue.

123
00:11:25,030 --> 00:11:28,760
Look. Zhou Siyue is over there.

124
00:11:28,760 --> 00:11:31,060
You are lying.

125
00:11:32,450 --> 00:11:34,250
Ding Xian.

126
00:11:45,356 --> 00:11:46,722
Come here.

127
00:11:46,722 --> 00:11:47,680
You two are ridiculous.

128
00:11:47,680 --> 00:11:50,301
Siyue and I searched every store, and we still couldn't find you.

129
00:11:51,050 --> 00:11:53,380
I'll take her back first.

130
00:11:54,780 --> 00:11:55,970
Hey!

131
00:11:56,810 --> 00:11:58,610
