134
00:12:06,400 --> 00:12:09,240
Why would I care about you?

135
00:12:11,660 --> 00:12:14,000
You are going to care about me.

136
00:12:14,000 --> 00:12:16,480
I want you to care about me all the time.

137
00:12:18,930 --> 00:12:20,083
