144
00:12:42,020 --> 00:12:45,130
I'll let you walk in front from now on, all right?

145
00:12:53,819 --> 00:12:57,249
It doesn't matter who's behind,

146
00:12:57,249 --> 00:13:00,710
I will not be able to walk with you again.

147
00:13:06,010 --> 00:13:08,800
Get up first, will you?

148
00:13:11,370 --> 00:13:13,070
Come on.

149
00:13:15,739 --> 00:13:17,439
Hop on.

150
00:13:27,740 --> 00:13:32,842
Didn't we agree that we will face everything together?

151
00:13:36,340 --> 00:13:38,470
Siyue.

152
00:13:39,370 --> 00:13:42,260
Zhou Siyue.

153
00:13:42,260 --> 00:13:44,423
I'm here.

154
00:13:44,423 --> 00:13:47,067
I've always been thinking

155
00:13:47,067 --> 00:13:52,560
about what we would look like when we grow up.

156
00:13:53,740 --> 00:13:58,050
Would we be leading a simple and happy life

157
00:13:58,050 --> 00:14:01,966
as we did in high school?

158
00:14:04,980 --> 00:14:06,980
I think so.

159
00:14:07,660 --> 00:14:09,990
You are lying.

160
00:14:09,990 --> 00:14:14,600
When have people ever stayed the same after they are separated?

161
00:14:14,600 --> 00:14:20,620
Are we going to become strangers one day?

162
00:14:20,620 --> 00:14:24,000
Stop the nonsense. You are drunk.

163
00:14:24,000 --> 00:14:26,890
I'm not drunk.

164
00:14:31,830 --> 00:14:37,290
Zhou Siyue, have you heard a saying?

165
00:14:37,290 --> 00:14:40,640
Don't worry when the cloud covers the moon.

166
00:14:40,640 --> 00:14:44,440
You are brighter than the stars.

167
00:14:46,060 --> 00:14:51,970
Your future is as bright as the stars.

168
00:14:52,740 --> 00:14:54,980
You are silly.

169
00:14:55,810 --> 00:14:58,780
Stars don't shine.

170
00:14:58,780 --> 00:15:01,220
I don't care.

171
00:15:07,780 --> 00:15:12,310
I said they do, and that's what they do.

172
00:15:23,350 --> 00:15:25,070
Silly.

173
00:15:31,460 --> 00:15:33,260
Open your mouth.

174
00:15:37,180 --> 00:15:40,090
