182
00:16:05,490 --> 00:16:10,750
Hey, hey, hey! It's okay.

183
00:16:10,750 --> 00:16:13,530
It's just that I can't bully you or make you suffer again.

184
00:16:13,530 --> 00:16:15,200
I'm fine.

185
00:16:15,200 --> 00:16:17,265
You just keep lying.

186
00:16:17,265 --> 00:16:19,610
You've been lying since we were young.

187
00:16:19,610 --> 00:16:21,552
