226
00:19:00,400 --> 00:19:02,100
All right.

227
00:19:02,100 --> 00:19:05,050
We are going to see each other every month.

228
00:19:05,050 --> 00:19:06,390
All right.

229
00:19:06,390 --> 00:19:08,680
