242
00:20:32,640 --> 00:20:34,707
Get up now!

243
00:20:36,320 --> 00:20:38,400
How did you do in the exam?

244
00:20:38,400 --> 00:20:40,483
Have you estimated your score yet?

245
00:20:44,133 --> 00:20:46,133
Not yet.

246
00:20:47,720 --> 00:20:50,941
Mom, I'm going to freshen up.

247
00:21:16,730 --> 00:21:21,550

248
00:21:21,550 --> 00:21:24,200

249
00:22:19,840 --> 00:22:23,530
Ding Xian, your teacher said that you would get into

250
00:22:23,530 --> 00:22:25,950
a top university in Hangzhou.

251
00:22:26,490 --> 00:22:30,990
Mom, I don't want to choose a university.

252
00:22:30,990 --> 00:22:32,460
What did you say?

253
00:22:32,460 --> 00:22:35,180
I said that I'm not going to choose a university.

254
00:22:36,820 --> 00:22:38,210
I want to repeat the third year.

255
00:22:38,210 --> 00:22:41,400
Instead of going to a top university,

256
00:22:41,400 --> 00:22:43,200
you want to spend money and redo the third year.

257
00:22:43,200 --> 00:22:45,190
Have you become a nerd?

258
00:22:45,190 --> 00:22:48,130
I could have done better in the exam.

259
00:22:48,130 --> 00:22:49,510
I can't let this go.

260
00:22:49,510 --> 00:22:51,210
I won't agree with that.

261
00:22:51,210 --> 00:22:53,200
I will ask your teacher to choose a university for you right now.

262
00:22:53,200 --> 00:22:54,730
Don't even think about repeating the third year.

263
00:22:54,730 --> 00:22:58,630
Mom, can you stop meddling?

264
00:22:58,630 --> 00:23:01,760
This is my life, not yours.

265
00:23:02,250 --> 00:23:05,030
Can you let me decide this time?

266
00:23:05,030 --> 00:23:08,770
I can live with the consequences whether they are good or bad.

267
00:23:08,770 --> 00:23:10,520
All right?

268
00:23:12,600 --> 00:23:14,600
Fine.

269
00:23:15,700 --> 00:23:19,820
I will never care about anything you do from now on.

270
00:23:25,250 --> 00:23:27,160
Don't worry.

271
00:23:27,160 --> 00:23:30,850
I've packed everything.

272
00:23:30,850 --> 00:23:33,590
We will be with you this afternoon.

273
00:23:34,660 --> 00:23:38,560
