274
00:23:40,330 --> 00:23:43,930
All right. That's all.

275
00:23:46,750 --> 00:23:50,750
What's going on, Mom? Are you going somewhere?

276
00:23:54,090 --> 00:23:57,230
Siyue, come here and sit.

277
00:23:57,230 --> 00:23:59,820
I need to talk to you about something.

278
00:24:02,250 --> 00:24:04,050
What happened?

279
00:24:05,420 --> 00:24:11,620
Siyue, we are going to Jiangling soon.

280
00:24:14,420 --> 00:24:19,420
Is it because something happened to Dad?

281
00:24:22,460 --> 00:24:27,010
I can't explain it in a few words.

282
00:24:27,010 --> 00:24:29,880
All right, got it.

283
00:24:38,460 --> 00:24:41,860
Mom, I need to go out shortly. I will be back soon.

284
00:24:41,860 --> 00:24:43,520
Go.

285
00:25:03,769 --> 00:25:06,290
I didn't do well in the exam.

286
00:25:09,210 --> 00:25:11,580
I can't go to Jiangling.

287
00:25:13,249 --> 00:25:15,590
So, where are you going?

288
00:25:16,261 --> 00:25:18,530
I'm going to...

289
00:25:19,780 --> 00:25:21,230
repeat the third year.

290
00:25:21,230 --> 00:25:23,230
Repeat the third year?

291
00:25:27,230 --> 00:25:30,230
You can wait for me in Huaqing.

292
00:25:30,970 --> 00:25:34,390
Maybe if I outdo myself,

293
00:25:36,130 --> 00:25:38,600
I will be joining you.

294
00:25:46,270 --> 00:25:48,070
All right.

295
00:25:52,230 --> 00:25:55,960
I have another thing to tell you.

296
00:25:59,210 --> 00:26:01,930
I might be leaving soon.

297
00:26:07,353 --> 00:26:10,413
Are you coming back this summer?

298
00:26:11,180 --> 00:26:15,480
I'm afraid that... I won't be able to come back.

299
00:26:18,200 --> 00:26:20,200
Fine.

300
00:26:24,720 --> 00:26:27,290
I will miss you.

301
00:26:40,330 --> 00:26:42,690
I have to go now.

302
00:26:43,360 --> 00:26:46,433
I'm starting the third year all over again tomorrow.

303
00:26:46,433 --> 00:26:48,333
Wait.

304
00:26:50,750 --> 00:26:53,620
I have a parting gift for you.

305
00:27:06,180 --> 00:27:12,280
Isn't this the robot called D2-T3 you showed me last time?

306
00:27:13,700 --> 00:27:17,800
Not bad. You still remember that.

307
00:27:19,130 --> 00:27:22,190
Why did you call it D2-T3?

308
00:27:22,190 --> 00:27:25,240
It's a random name.

309
00:27:27,490 --> 00:27:30,700
I'm going to give it a name.

310
00:27:31,850 --> 00:27:35,170
All right. What do you want to call it?

311
00:27:39,610 --> 00:27:41,410
April.

312
00:27:43,090 --> 00:27:45,190
April?

313
00:27:47,300 --> 00:27:49,760
 I will always remember

314
00:27:49,760 --> 00:27:52,750
 the summer when I was 18

315
00:27:52,750 --> 00:27:57,390
 that was excruciatingly hot and tough.

316
00:27:57,970 --> 00:28:03,630
 Everything I knew was saying goodbye to me and leaving me.

317
00:28:03,630 --> 00:28:08,890
 All I could do was face reality

318
00:28:08,890 --> 00:28:13,490
 and say goodbye with a smile.

319
00:28:36,420 --> 00:28:40,320
Xianxian, I would like to discuss something with you.

320
00:28:40,320 --> 00:28:43,300
Director Wang from the senior year has always been the class adviser of honor classes.

321
00:28:43,300 --> 00:28:45,610
They have a high university enrollment rate.

322
00:28:45,610 --> 00:28:47,570
Your mom and I discussed it.

323
00:28:47,570 --> 00:28:52,200
How about you repeat the third year in his class?

324
00:28:52,200 --> 00:28:55,720
Great. I've also heard that Mr. Wang is excellent.

325
00:28:55,720 --> 00:28:58,420
I might make more progress in his class.

326
00:28:58,420 --> 00:29:01,320
All right. I should go now.

327
00:29:01,320 --> 00:29:02,940
You should also head to school after breakfast.

328
00:29:02,940 --> 00:29:07,480
Dad, I'm also done. Let's go together.

329
00:29:08,240 --> 00:29:12,596
All right. Come. Let's go. I'll carry that for you.

330
00:29:13,010 --> 00:29:16,095
Come on. We are leaving now.

331
00:29:18,340 --> 00:29:21,440

332
00:29:23,710 --> 00:29:27,480

333
00:29:31,440 --> 00:29:35,430
All right. Guys, I'll make this short.

334
00:29:35,430 --> 00:29:39,700
You all understand the pressure of the third year.

335
00:29:39,700 --> 00:29:43,280
I'm not going to say big words here.

336
00:29:43,280 --> 00:29:47,430
But I do have one request.

337
00:29:49,510 --> 00:29:54,090
Carefully write down the university you desire

338
00:29:54,090 --> 00:29:58,920
and start to work towards it today.

339
00:29:58,920 --> 00:30:02,900
We have several students repeating the third year.

340
00:30:02,900 --> 00:30:07,000
I hope they can face their past

341
00:30:07,000 --> 00:30:09,130
and review themselves.

342
00:30:09,130 --> 00:30:11,910
Make better choices this time.

343
00:30:16,180 --> 00:30:18,660
 As the third year starts again,

344
00:30:18,660 --> 00:30:22,210
 I feel like everyone is drifting away from me.

345
00:30:22,920 --> 00:30:27,230
 They are all walking on the right path towards the future,

346
00:30:27,230 --> 00:30:32,740
 and I'm the only one off track.

347
00:30:32,740 --> 00:30:38,000
 I'm missing Zhou Siyue and everyone else.

348
00:30:38,912 --> 00:30:42,740
 As shredded and obscure

349
00:30:42,740 --> 00:30:45,290
 as the days are,

350
00:30:45,290 --> 00:30:48,210
 I can never let myself relax for one second.

351
00:30:48,210 --> 00:30:50,870
 I'm worried that once I stop,

352
00:30:50,870 --> 00:30:54,120
 countless people will surpass me

353
00:30:54,120 --> 00:30:56,440
 and make me a stepping stone.

354
00:31:00,850 --> 00:31:03,850

355
00:31:03,850 --> 00:31:08,870
Professor Ye, hello. I'm Zhou Zongtang's son.

356
00:31:08,870 --> 00:31:11,190
You must be Siyue.

357
00:31:11,190 --> 00:31:14,840
Old Zhou told me a lot about you. We are finally meeting today.

358
00:31:14,840 --> 00:31:19,130
Yes. I've heard that you and my dad are good friends.

359
00:31:19,130 --> 00:31:22,350
That's why I came unnoticed today.

360
00:31:22,350 --> 00:31:24,200
Not at all.

361
00:31:24,780 --> 00:31:27,090
Here is the thing, Professor Ye.

362
00:31:28,150 --> 00:31:33,060
Do you know what happened to my dad?

363
00:31:39,010 --> 00:31:42,220
Ding Xian, is Huaqing your target?

364
00:31:43,210 --> 00:31:44,910
Yes.

365
00:31:47,180 --> 00:31:52,380
Ding Xian, a year is not too long or too short.

366
00:31:52,380 --> 00:31:54,470
If your target is Huaqing,

367
00:31:54,470 --> 00:31:58,080
you will need to put in more effort than the others.

368
00:31:58,080 --> 00:32:00,080
I know.

369
00:32:01,460 --> 00:32:03,360
And I will.

370
00:32:03,940 --> 00:32:05,090
- Hello.
 - Hello.

371
00:32:05,090 --> 00:32:07,790
This is a letter for Zhou Zongtang. Please sign it.

372
00:32:07,790 --> 00:32:09,690
- Thank you.
 - Thank you.

373
00:32:10,460 --> 00:32:12,060
Eat your food.

374
00:32:14,090 --> 00:32:15,790
Is it for me?

375
00:32:15,790 --> 00:32:17,900
Yes.

376
00:32:26,533 --> 00:32:28,307

377
00:32:32,900 --> 00:32:34,400
You guys eat. It's okay.

378
00:32:34,400 --> 00:32:36,120
I need to make a phone call.

379
00:32:40,130 --> 00:32:43,110
Mr. Wang. Sorry.

380
00:32:43,110 --> 00:32:45,170
I've been troubling you with this.

381
00:32:46,010 --> 00:32:49,090
 Zhou's thesis

382
00:32:49,090 --> 00:32:51,680
 was reported for suspicion of plagiarism and fraud.

383
00:32:52,310 --> 00:32:54,970
 He's under investigation now.

384
00:32:57,640 --> 00:32:58,940
Siyue.

385
00:32:59,710 --> 00:33:01,190
What are you thinking about?

386
00:33:01,190 --> 00:33:02,790
Have some food.

387
00:33:04,230 --> 00:33:06,130
You too.

388
00:33:08,190 --> 00:33:09,710
 I've seen everything through now.

389
00:33:10,400 --> 00:33:13,110
 There will be a day when the truth comes out.

390
00:33:26,026 --> 00:33:27,526
Dad.

391
00:33:28,780 --> 00:33:30,180
What's happening?

392
00:33:33,063 --> 00:33:34,850
I've been suffering from minor hypoglycemia.

393
00:33:34,850 --> 00:33:37,060
A doctor has prescribed some medicine for me.

394
00:33:37,060 --> 00:33:38,560
Don't worry.

395
00:33:39,490 --> 00:33:41,660
Go back and rest.

396
00:33:43,370 --> 00:33:44,770
Dad,

397
00:33:45,580 --> 00:33:47,810
I went to see Professor Ye today.

398
00:33:56,300 --> 00:33:57,500
I know...

399
00:33:58,300 --> 00:33:59,780
that you are worried

400
00:33:59,780 --> 00:34:01,700
that I will be affected in school.

401
00:34:02,370 --> 00:34:03,920
But I'm not afraid.

402
00:34:04,780 --> 00:34:06,380
I believe in you.

403
00:34:12,370 --> 00:34:13,970
Sorry.

404
00:34:15,850 --> 00:34:17,870
I've brought this on you and your mom.

405
00:34:19,220 --> 00:34:21,300
We are a family.

406
00:34:23,130 --> 00:34:25,300
We are supposed to share burdens.

407
00:34:28,530 --> 00:34:33,050
Besides, there are so many professors in Huaqing,

408
00:34:33,050 --> 00:34:35,530
people may not know you at all,

409
00:34:35,530 --> 00:34:37,600
let alone me.

410
00:34:39,810 --> 00:34:41,770
You haven't had anything yet, right?

411
00:34:41,770 --> 00:34:43,690
I'll warm up the dishes.

412
00:35:24,330 --> 00:35:26,790
- Hello?
 - Hello?

413
00:35:27,691 --> 00:35:30,690
Have you got the result of the entrance examination today?

414
00:35:31,460 --> 00:35:33,060
How did it go?

415
00:35:34,910 --> 00:35:36,210
Not bad.

416
00:35:36,770 --> 00:35:39,580
I got a high place on the rankings.

417
00:35:40,230 --> 00:35:43,290
Why are you calling me all of a sudden?

418
00:35:43,290 --> 00:35:45,370
I just want to tell you that...

419
00:35:46,190 --> 00:35:48,110
I've sorted out everything here.

420
00:35:49,390 --> 00:35:51,840
And I will report to school tomorrow.

421
00:35:52,670 --> 00:35:54,070
 Don't worry about me.

422
00:35:55,190 --> 00:35:56,600
 How about you?

423
00:35:56,600 --> 00:35:58,220
 How are you doing in school?

424
00:36:03,850 --> 00:36:04,980
Ding Xian?

425
00:36:04,980 --> 00:36:06,780
What's wrong?

426
00:36:09,043 --> 00:36:10,850
I'm fine.

427
00:36:11,470 --> 00:36:13,230
My marks and ranking...

428
00:36:14,000 --> 00:36:15,560
in this exam...

429
00:36:16,430 --> 00:36:18,010
are both good.

430
00:36:19,371 --> 00:36:22,920
The teacher said that...

431
00:36:24,430 --> 00:36:26,360
I might get into Huaqing.

432
00:36:27,800 --> 00:36:28,800
 Oh, right!

433
00:36:29,670 --> 00:36:31,120
 Can you take some photos for me

434
00:36:31,120 --> 00:36:33,120
 when you arrive at Huaqing?

435
00:36:34,770 --> 00:36:36,430
You are silly.

436
00:36:37,260 --> 00:36:38,970
Of course, I can.

437
00:36:40,180 --> 00:36:43,030
I want to know what Huaqing looks like.

438
00:36:44,570 --> 00:36:46,110
You'll know when you get here.

439
00:36:47,800 --> 00:36:51,350
I hope everything can go well.

440
00:36:53,630 --> 00:36:56,060
Are you really okay?

441
00:36:59,230 --> 00:37:01,060
I'm just a little tired.

442
00:37:01,700 --> 00:37:03,200
I feel sleepy.

443
00:37:03,900 --> 00:37:05,870
Then go to bed.

444
00:37:07,900 --> 00:37:10,110
Everything will be fine.

445
00:37:14,230 --> 00:37:16,560
Everything will be fine.

446
00:37:27,491 --> 00:37:29,091
Siyue.

447
00:37:31,530 --> 00:37:33,020
Mom.

448
00:37:33,020 --> 00:37:34,120
You are still up.

449
00:37:35,760 --> 00:37:38,600
I just finished the laundry and I'm about to hang them on the balcony.

450
00:37:39,420 --> 00:37:41,510
Why are you still up?

451
00:37:44,050 --> 00:37:46,400
Why are you putting these away?

452
00:37:47,660 --> 00:37:49,460
These are all useless objects.

453
00:37:49,460 --> 00:37:50,980
I want to see if I can sell them.

454
00:37:50,980 --> 00:37:53,080
Aren't these your treasures?

455
00:37:54,370 --> 00:37:56,320
That's when I was young.

456
00:37:56,320 --> 00:37:58,170
I'm all grown up now.

457
00:38:01,436 --> 00:38:03,136
Right, Mom.

458
00:38:03,190 --> 00:38:05,130
I might need to go back to Shenhai

459
00:38:05,130 --> 00:38:07,210
before school starts.

460
00:38:18,370 --> 00:38:19,770
Ding Juncong!

461
00:38:20,270 --> 00:38:23,230
Did you stay up all night playing games again?

462
00:38:23,230 --> 00:38:24,590
It's a weekend.

463
00:38:25,090 --> 00:38:27,020
What's wrong with playing games?

464
00:38:27,020 --> 00:38:29,210
You are about to be in junior high soon.

465
00:38:29,840 --> 00:38:32,500
You need to focus on studying.

466
00:38:32,500 --> 00:38:35,050
If you could learn half as hard as your sister does,

467
00:38:35,050 --> 00:38:36,290
I will never say anything about you.

468
00:38:36,290 --> 00:38:38,390
My sis has become a nerd already.

469
00:38:38,390 --> 00:38:39,390
Stop the nonsense.

470
00:38:40,080 --> 00:38:43,120
Xianxian, did you stay up late studying again?

471
00:38:43,920 --> 00:38:45,130
Yeah.

472
00:38:46,770 --> 00:38:48,950
Mr. Wang told me that you have made

473
00:38:48,950 --> 00:38:50,990
huge progress a few days ago.

474
00:38:50,990 --> 00:38:52,190
You did really well in the exam.

475
00:38:52,190 --> 00:38:53,670
But I have to warn you,

476
00:38:53,670 --> 00:38:54,910
don't work too hard.

477
00:38:54,910 --> 00:38:57,191
You need to relax occasionally so that you won't break.

478
00:38:57,240 --> 00:38:58,460
Okay.

479
00:38:58,460 --> 00:39:00,160
I understand.

480
00:39:03,850 --> 00:39:05,550
I'm going back to my room now.

481
00:39:06,770 --> 00:39:08,180
Is that all you are going to eat?

482
00:39:08,180 --> 00:39:09,780
I'm full.

483
00:39:11,120 --> 00:39:12,710
She can't keep this up.

484
00:39:12,710 --> 00:39:15,120
Her spirit is getting worse.

485
00:39:15,940 --> 00:39:18,180
I heard her talking in her dream last night.

486
00:39:18,180 --> 00:39:20,140
She was reciting formulas in her dream.

487
00:39:20,788 --> 00:39:21,840
There's nothing I can do about it.

488
00:39:21,840 --> 00:39:24,000
Why don't you go talk to her?

489
00:39:24,000 --> 00:39:25,400
I'm not saying anything.

490
00:39:26,220 --> 00:39:27,800
I didn't want her to repeat the third year

491
00:39:27,800 --> 00:39:30,710
because I didn't want her to be stuck in this.

492
00:39:30,710 --> 00:39:32,120
What's the point of all this?

493
00:39:32,120 --> 00:39:33,390
Enough. Stop talking.

494
00:39:33,390 --> 00:39:34,390
It won't do anything now.

495
00:39:35,040 --> 00:39:36,040
What should we do?

496
00:39:37,380 --> 00:39:38,660
I don't know.

497
00:39:39,390 --> 00:39:41,040
I know my sister

498
00:39:41,040 --> 00:39:43,330
might listen to this one person.

499
00:39:43,330 --> 00:39:44,930
Who is it?

500
00:39:50,260 --> 00:39:51,361
Mom, I'm not hungry.

501
00:39:51,361 --> 00:39:53,710
I'll skip lunch. Don't wait for me.

502
00:39:53,710 --> 00:39:55,500
 Xianxian, it's me.

503
00:40:03,330 --> 00:40:04,770
Senior Brother!

504
00:40:04,770 --> 00:40:06,800
I thought you were in Jiangling right now.

505
00:40:06,800 --> 00:40:08,150
I'm here to visit your parents

506
00:40:08,150 --> 00:40:10,000
and check up on you by the way.

507
00:40:10,000 --> 00:40:11,200
Come on, let's go take a walk.

508
00:40:11,980 --> 00:40:14,500
Don't lock yourself in your room studying.

509
00:40:18,390 --> 00:40:20,830
Did my parents ask you to come?

510
00:40:23,050 --> 00:40:24,970
They are worried about you.

511
00:40:26,740 --> 00:40:28,440
I'm fine.

512
00:40:30,950 --> 00:40:32,450
Repeating the third year...

513
00:40:33,630 --> 00:40:35,030
must be tough.

514
00:40:37,570 --> 00:40:40,270
A lot of people are living a tougher life than I am.

515
00:40:42,430 --> 00:40:44,550
This is nothing.

516
00:40:49,390 --> 00:40:50,690
Senior Brother,

517
00:40:51,390 --> 00:40:52,790
do you know that...

518
00:40:55,230 --> 00:40:58,470
there's a girl in our class named Lin You?

519
00:40:59,910 --> 00:41:01,870
She's repeating the third year for the third time.

520
00:41:03,000 --> 00:41:05,320
Her target has always been Nanjing University.

521
00:41:06,260 --> 00:41:10,470
But she's doing worse during each year.

522
00:41:11,670 --> 00:41:14,390
I think she's the most painstaking

523
00:41:14,390 --> 00:41:16,410
and hard-working student in our class.

524
00:41:17,000 --> 00:41:19,430
But the harder she works, the more often she screws up.

525
00:41:20,120 --> 00:41:22,950
She once had a meltdown right in our classroom

526
00:41:22,950 --> 00:41:26,180
and tore up all the books and papers.

527
00:41:29,850 --> 00:41:31,250
Repeating the third year...

528
00:41:33,760 --> 00:41:35,080
is terrifying.

529
00:41:37,630 --> 00:41:39,030
Xianxian,

530
00:41:40,560 --> 00:41:42,000
is this what you are thinking about?

531
00:41:45,120 --> 00:41:46,120
Actually,

532
00:41:47,000 --> 00:41:48,480
if you are tired,

533
00:41:49,290 --> 00:41:51,630
if you want to take a break,

534
00:41:53,203 --> 00:41:54,520
no one will blame you.

535
00:42:00,870 --> 00:42:01,870
Senior Brother,

536
00:42:04,600 --> 00:42:05,670
I'm so tired.

537
00:42:06,646 --> 00:42:09,170
I'm really tired.

538
00:42:34,490 --> 00:42:43,760

539
00:42:46,815 --> 00:42:52,105
♫  The night breeze sweeps over your hair  ♫

540
00:42:52,153 --> 00:42:55,465
♫  Seeing your smile  ♫

541
00:42:57,362 --> 00:43:01,648
♫  It makes me want to jump in your arms  ♫

542
00:43:01,648 --> 00:43:05,405
♫  You make me smile unknowingly  ♫

543
00:43:06,793 --> 00:43:12,655
♫  That wonderful taste is the chemistry of love  ♫

544
00:43:12,655 --> 00:43:15,993
♫  Lean on your shoulder  ♫

545
00:43:17,249 --> 00:43:23,028
♫  My longing for you has left a beam of light in my heart  ♫

546
00:43:23,028 --> 00:43:26,105
♫  Reminding me of the love you gave me  ♫

547
00:43:27,102 --> 00:43:30,275
♫  I want to go somewhere far away with you  ♫

548
00:43:30,275 --> 00:43:32,868
♫  Finding each other's sea  ♫

549
00:43:32,868 --> 00:43:36,565
♫  Let the light of love heal the pain  ♫

550
00:43:37,881 --> 00:43:40,738
